Characterization of paralogous uncx transcription factor encoding genes in 
zebrafish.

Nittoli V(1), Fortunato AE(2), Fasano G(1), Coppola U(1), Gentile A(3), Maiella 
S(4), Langellotto F(5), Porreca I(6), De Paolo R(1), Marino R(1), Fiengo M(7), 
