Wijnen BFM(1)(2), Thielen FW(3), Konings S(4), Feenstra T(5), Van Der Gaag 
M(6)(7), Veling W(4), De Haan L(8), Ising H(7), Hiligsmann M(9), Evers 
SMAA(1)(9), Smit F(1)(10)(11), Lokkerbol J(1)(12).

Author information:
(1)Centre of Economic Evaluation (Trimbos Institute), Netherlands Institute of 
